# Look up objects in the semantic map by label.
# Returns every confirmed instance (>= min_observations) of that label, so the
# caller can disambiguate multiple same-label objects. Empty -> not found.
# Each match carries its map position, confidence, label, and last_seen
# (DetectedObject3D.header.stamp). matches are sorted by confidence, descending.
string label
---
DetectedObject3D[] matches
